Industries


Investment Services & Portfolio Management

Trusts & Funds




Company Description


Charlemagne Capital (IOM) Ltd., part of Fiera Capital Corp., is a company headquartered in Douglas, UK. The firm provides investment advice. It was founded by James Mellon. Jane Davidson Nairn McAndry is the current CEO, occupying that position since 2007.




